  "articleContent": "<div><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://hw-media-cdn-mingchao.kurogame.com/object/1733846400000/2qcfff86r4nwud914i-1733884134872.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"510\" data-media-source=\"production_G152_en\" data-desc=\"succ\"></div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div>\n<div data-page-id=\"TbcgdHo3Lo69A7xql0rcKZSFnMh\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"false\">\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Dear Rovers,</span><br><br><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Due to design errors, certain merchandise items (including Yinlin Acrylic Stand, Yinlin Clear Card, and Yinlin Ticket-style Card) will not be available during the Animate x Wuthering Waves pop-up event as originally planned. The re-design process for these items is currently underway to align with the initial plan. All collaboration merchandise, including the above 3 items, will be made available for online purchase after the event. Further details will be announced at a later date.</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">List of Unavailable Items for Purchaseâ–¼</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><br>1. Yinlin Acrylic Stand</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://hw-media-cdn-mingchao.kurogame.com/object/1733846400000/veyvmt0reueaeut5h7-1733884240053.png\" width=\"800\" height=\"1191\" data-media-source=\"production_G152_en\" data-desc=\"succ\"></span><br><br><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">2. Yinlin Clear Card</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://hw-media-cdn-mingchao.kurogame.com/object/1733846400000/48rtdgxdwgo4tkprpk-1733884300814.png\" width=\"800\" height=\"987\" data-media-source=\"production_G152_en\" data-desc=\"succ\"></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">3. Yinlin 